a spouse's new opportunity, personal growth,

6
00:00:17.109 --> 00:00:18.647
those you can't control.

7
00:00:18.647 --> 00:00:22.613
But what you don't want is people leaving because of

8
00:00:22.613 --> 00:00:25.724
you and what is in your control.

