00:00:25.724 --> 00:00:28.906
Also regarding promotions and salary and benefits,

10
00:00:28.906 --> 00:00:32.153
that also may not totally be in your control,

11
00:00:32.153 --> 00:00:35.724
but find out what influence you have in those areas so you can

12
00:00:35.724 --> 00:00:37.724
use them as tools to be more successful.

13
00:00:37.724 --> 00:00:43.724
So talk to your manager or human resources and find out more about those ideas.

