Now if you can align your IT activities to the business then people will

15
00:00:48.124 --> 00:00:51.724
feel more connected to the business and their job.

16
00:00:51.724 --> 00:00:54.724
This will create better motivation and passion and therefore people

17
00:00:54.724 --> 00:00:58.724
like to hang around and you'll retain more people.

